{"tid":657390,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"家姐好野","createTime":"2018-05-08T05:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T07:42:52.000Z","uid":182832,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f151dd385b145fe4a6bd7adac022dd0f41b870bb","tid":657390,"uid":182832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"話說咁樣的！我好鐘意細佬佢個ex 既。 錫到佢地當自己既仔女咁。<br />\n細佬同佢個ex呢就好地地既， 成家都好開心。但條仆街仔偷食，引左件臭雞上身， 搞到一鑊屎，個咁好既女友仲激L走左。 <br />\n<br />\n自從臭雞小三坐正。細佬唔理屋企不但只，仲成日幫隻臭雞講野。 一日到黑想洗我腦。 我話你知冇可能！ <br />\n本來呢場戰爭持續，我已經想像到萬一佢地一齊、甚至結婚，計劃緊要點玩死佢呢條八婆。總之我成家都夾好晒唔會俾好面口佢睇，實行唔當佢係人！ 點知劇情大反轉，尋晚終於發現細佬綠左！帶左帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =我 、 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =細佬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你之前掉左我野阿？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：掉咪掉囉。總之唔同隻臭雞分手， 何止掉你公仔。 我連你都趕走都得阿！ <br />\n<br />\n呢隻臭雞之前要拆散人時寄隻公仔黎。我特登掉左佢既掛號郵件通知卡。（本小姐一早睇到你fb寄公仔啦。我點會俾你寄到我細佬手上。 ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：多謝你， 你放心都得啦。分左手！佢俾帽我帶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：yeah!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩仲特別用句咁打電話同臭雞講返兩句道別下！ <br />\n我都忍得你耐啦， 仲唔可以鬧下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n臭雞， 睇到就唔好再死纏爛打啦。 咁賤做第三者啦， 專搶人條仔都算， 搶到仲要派帽。自作自受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然心疼細佬green 左 ，但<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好開心囉！ 忍唔住要開post普天同慶下"},{"pid":"07298e3d93bf03c8e00a6ed38ae1f7c8fcbab494","tid":657390,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"家姐都係你最錫我！"},{"pid":"8bbc6fd2a9e5431afed0ca8516fb9be7146b65ac","tid":657390,"uid":182832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07298e3d93bf03c8e00a6ed38ae1f7c8fcbab494","tid":657390,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"家姐都係你最錫我！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133031a443cd96333efa8c087db36fa353f077d2","tid":657390,"uid":138138,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"阿哥你扮完女人未<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/133730_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F133730_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c4a3126c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71da08efd9087369ccc74bc036eaa5304e17f811","tid":657390,"uid":182832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"133031a443cd96333efa8c087db36fa353f077d2","tid":657390,"uid":138138,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"阿哥你扮完女人未<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/133730_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://